- it’s a 3 min ride⁣
- it’s kid & adult friendly⁣
- best to go at night⁣

@8bitbitesusa is a 100% halal restaurant in bed-stuy & it brings all the 80’s & 90’s nostalgia! they have smash burgers, fried chicken sandwiches, tenders & my fav — 𝐂𝐄𝐑𝐄𝐀𝐋 𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐊𝐒𝐇𝐀𝐊𝐄𝐒 😮‍💨😅⁣⁣
⁣
(everything on the menu can add up to more than $10 but it doesn’t hurt to share this gem 🥳)⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
👾games are free to play⁣⁣
👾a huge selection of games from mario to tetris & more!⁣⁣
👾30min game limit⁣⁣
👾put your name on the wait list if the game tables are full⁣⁣
👾40 seats & 7 multiplayer game stations⁣⁣

this really is a 𝐁𝐎𝐓𝐓𝐎𝐌𝐋𝐄𝐒𝐒 𝐁𝐑𝐔𝐍𝐂𝐇 experience 🤪🥂⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@chansonlesalon is a beautiful parisian style restaurant in tribeca offering an extensive brunch menu & delicious bottomless drinks. you’re literally just making your own mimosas to your liking 😗. they have blooming teas & brunch cocktails. this also turns into a cocktail bar after 5PM from tues to sat & you can try out a zodiac themed cocktail! 🤪⁣
⁣
we almost didn’t survive this brunch bcs they just kept on handing us bottles of prosecco 🙃 but the chicken & waffles were so good & the hot sauce was such a nice touch. the steak & eggs were cooked perfectly & not a single bite was left. ⁣
⁣

this free exhibit is for the MANGA lovers 📖🤩⁣
⁣
@ginzasonypark presents 𝐌𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐀 𝐢𝐧 𝐍𝐞𝐰 𝐘𝐨𝐫𝐤 & this exhibit is a manga lovers dream! this exhibit shows a fusion of sony’s many technologies with original MANGA curated for this event by 6 amazing groups of talented japanese artists!⁣⁣
⁣⁣
there are 2 floors to discover all of the artists artworks like 𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐧𝐢𝐮𝐦 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐝𝐞’𝐬 “dream pill” where you get to interact with the art & essentially “walk on water” & you’ll see the ripples with each step you take! 𝐡𝐢𝐤𝐚𝐫𝐮 𝐢𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐣𝐨’𝐬 beautiful, colorful & whimsical illustrations.⁣⁣
⁣⁣
𝐭𝐚𝐤𝐚𝐤𝐮𝐫𝐚𝐤𝐚𝐳𝐮𝐤𝐢’𝐬 “the pilgrim’s guide to video games” where he uses all forms of technology & gives you the video game experience of reading the manga on a console!⁣⁣
⁣⁣
along with 𝐦𝐚𝐬𝐚𝐧𝐨𝐛𝐮 𝐡𝐢𝐫𝐚𝐨𝐤𝐚’𝐬 unique drawings where you can take a piece of his art home by grabbing a free oolong tea from the vending machine! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣

💸:⁣⁣ ⁣⁣free / until november 5, 2023⁣⁣
